infos.name: Nadia Lefebvre
infos.introText: Hello! I'm a skilled frontend developer with experience in React and a background as a language specialist. I bring structure, attention to detail, strong communication skills, and a passion for solving problems. I am a quick learner, always eager to improve and take on new challenges. My goal is to create impactful products that matter and contribute to a knowledge-sharing culture within the workplace.
